Containing an area of TWO HUNDRED FORTY ONE THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED EIGHTY SIX (241,286) SQUARE METERS, more or less, subject to future survey.

All points referred to are indicated in the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 40 cm., bearings true.

In order to facilitate the early development of the area for the introduction of the Slum Improvement and Resettlement (SIR) Program, the National Housing Authority, in coordination with the Land Management Services, DENR, Region VI, Iloilo City, is hereby ordered to immediately conduct the necessary subdivision survey of the same into appropriate homelots, roadlots and community facilities for public use.

The National Housing Authority is hereby given the authority to develop, administer and dispose of these lots in accordance with LOI Nos. 555, 557, as amended by LOI No. 686, and for this purpose shall evolve, prepare and implement a comprehensive development plan under existing guidelines and procedures.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Iloilo, this 10th day of March, in the year or Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety one.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) OSCAR M. ORBOS Executive Secretary

